name: Drift Car
description: Experience the thrill of driving a Drift Car with this highly detailed toy car. It features realistic design, opening doors, and a high-quality finish.

name: Ferrari 488 GTB
description: Get ready to race with the iconic Ferrari 488 GTB toy car. It's beautifully crafted, with a sleek design, smooth wheels, and authentic Ferrari branding.

name: Porsche 911 GT3 RS
description: Immerse yourself in luxury with the Porsche 911 GT3 RS toy car. It replicates the iconic Porsche design and offers a smooth driving experience.

name: Regular Fire Truck
description: Encourage eco-friendly play with the Fire Truck. It is made from recycled plastic, features a working ladder, and inspires creative storytelling and firefighting adventures.

name: Big Firefighter Truck
description: Let your child become a heroic firefighter with the Firefighter truck. It includes a fire truck, firefighter figure, and accessories for imaginative play and rescue missions.

name: Paw Patrol Marshall Fire Truck
description: Join Marshall from Paw Patrol on exciting rescue missions with the Marshall Fire Truck toy. It features a fun Paw Patrol theme, extendable ladder, and interactive lights and sounds.

name: Hot Wheels Car
description: Ignite your child's love for cars with the Hot Wheels Car. It includes 20 different die-cast cars with various designs and colors for endless racing and imaginative play.

name: Lightning McQueen
description: Race into the world of Disney Pixar Cars with the Lightning McQueen toy. It features a detailed character design, rolling wheels, and is perfect for recreating beloved movie moments.

name: Pull-Back Vehicles
description: Introduce learning and play with the Fisher-Price Laugh & Learn Pull-Back Vehicles. They feature friendly faces, pull-back action, and interactive phrases and songs to engage and entertain kids.
